name: DogeBonk
description: What is the project about? The "Doggy-Bonk" memecoin project token operates on the Ethereum blockchain, embracing a lighthearted and humorous approach. This whimsical concept sets it apart from more conventional projects in the blockchain ecosystem. History of your project.
